    {
      "id": "1446255838577692822",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2025-12-04T21:44:22.051+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": "2025-12-04T21:44:32.634+00:00",
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Looking at the doc : \n\"\"\"This comp area contained the protection diode and any other drain or source junction connected to this node.\"\"\"\n\nso `pplus + COMP` is perfectly valid and should be included in the `diodes` so I'm pretty sure that KLayout deck is wrong.",
